```json
{
"application": "Magpie",
"details": {
"description": "Magpie is a suite of scripts designed to launch Hadoop and other Big Data projects on traditional HPC systems.",
"software_requirements": {
"java": "/usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.8.0/",
"python": "/usr/bin/python",
"hadoop": {
"version": "2.7.3",
"home": "${HOME}/hadoop-${HADOOP_VERSION}",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/hadoop",
"conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf",
"daemon_heap_max": "2000",
"namenode_heap_max": "2000",
"environment_extra_path": "${HOME}/hadoop-my-environment"
},
"spark": {
"version": "2.4.3-bin-hadoop2.7",
"home": "${HOME}/spark-${SPARK_VERSION}",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/spark",
"conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf",
"worker_cores_per_node": "8",
"worker_memory_per_node": "16000",
"worker_directory": "/tmp/${USER}/spark/work",
"job_memory": "2048",
"driver_memory": "2048",
"daemon_heap_max": "2000",
"environment_extra_path": "${HOME}/spark-my-environment"
},
"resource_requirements": {
"pbs_node_count": "<my_node_count>",
"pbs_account": "<my_account_string>",
"pbs_partition": "<my_partition>",
"pbs_queue": "<my_batch_queue>",
"pbs_walltime": "<my_time_in_seconds_or_HH:MM:SS>",
"magpie_scripts_home": "${HOME}/magpie",
"magpie_local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",
"magpie_startup_time": "30",
"magpie_shutdown_time": "30",
"magpie_pre_job_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/pre-job-run-scripts/my-pre-job-script",
"magpie_post_job_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/post-job-run-scripts/my-post-job-script",
"magpie_pre_execute_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/pre-job-run-scripts/my-pre-job-script",
"magpie_post_execute_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/post-job-run-scripts/my-post-job-script",
"magpie_environment_variable_script": "${HOME}/my-job-env",
"magpie_environment_variable_script_shell": "/bin/bash",
"magpie_remote_cmd": "ssh",
"magpie_remote_cmd_opts": ""
}
}
}
```
